## NEW invoice workflow + delivery

1. `cp` modern template → `htsa-enrollment-{slug}.html`.  
2. Replace client fields (`<title>`, hero, billing, steps, Welcome, **`data-*`**, **`STORAGE_KEY`**, JS slug fallback).  
3. Adjust investment HTML **only** in the new file.  
4. Run verification checklist; **`grep`** stray names/contacts.  
5. **`git add`** **only** the new HTML (and rule/skill if edited in the **same** task) — never scratch/review artifacts.  
6. **`git commit`** + **`git push`** to **`origin/main`** (or the repo’s documented deploy branch) **unless** CJ explicitly says **draft only / do not push**. Live **closewithcjclay.com** pages come from this repository — skipping push is the usual cause of **404** on newly built invoice URLs.  
7. Return **exactly:** `https://closewithcjclay.com/htsa-enrollment-{slug}.html` — **only after** instantiate/`paste` output shows **`READY`** (live HTTP 200). Do not share the link before **`READY`**.  
   - **`htsa-instantiate-invoice.py --ship`** (and **`htsa-paste-invoice.py`**, which calls it) **polls the live URL** for up to **6 minutes** after push and only prints **`READY`** + the URL when **`HTTP 2xx`** — **do not send CJ the link until you see `READY`** (or run `sh scripts/check-enrollment-live.sh {slug}`).  
   - **Typo guard:** Links must use **`htsa-enrollment-`** (with **a**). The pattern **`hts-enrollment-`** (no **a**) **404s** except redirect stubs.  
   - **Manual check:** `sh scripts/check-enrollment-live.sh {slug}` — same poll loop, exits **0** when live.

